# Intelligent FAQ System

## Overview
This is a mini NLP project to retrieve answers for user queries.

## Features
- TF-IDF search
- Cosine similarity
- Top 3 results
- Search history
- Word2Vec demo

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Gensim

## Run Project
python final_project.py

## Learning
- NLP basics
- Search systems
- RAG concept